1. *Dečko* je došao na rođendan. (The boy came to the birthday.)

2. Mama je zamolila *dečka* da ode. (Mom asked the boy to leave.)

3. Njena *dečka* voli da igra fudbal. (Her boyfriend loves to play football.)

4. Svi su se smejali kad je *dečko* pao. (Everyone laughed when the boy fell.)

5. *Dečka* je zvala svog druga. (The girl called her friend.)

6. *Dečku* su poklonili roze kolač. (They gave the boy a pink cake.)

7. *Dečko* je umoran od čitanja knjige. (The boy is tired from reading a book.)

8. *Dečku* je bilo neprijatno da govori. (The boy was uncomfortable to talk.)